---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import anatomyImg from "../assets/images/access-1.webp";
---

<section id="advantages" class="relative overflow-hidden py-24 sm:py-32">
	<!-- Background glow -->
	<div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[800px] h-[800px] rounded-full bg-primary/5 blur-3xl"></div>

	<div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
		<!-- Section header -->
		<div class="reveal flex items-end justify-between gap-8 flex-wrap">
			<div>
				<span class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-primary">Почему калистеника</span>
				<h2 class="mt-4 text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl max-w-xl">
					МОЁ
					<span class="bg-linear-to-r from-brand-orange to-brand-gold bg-clip-text text-transparent">ПРЕДЛОЖЕНИЕ</span>
					ДЛЯ ВАС
				</h2>
			</div>
			<p class="max-w-md text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
				Выберите путь к новому телу. Какой бы ни была ваша цель, у меня есть <span class="text-foreground underline decoration-primary/50 underline-offset-4">индивидуальное решение</span> для вас.
			</p>
		</div>

		<!-- Bento grid -->
		<div class="reveal mt-16 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4">
			<!-- Card 1: Online Coaching (tall) -->
			<div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-border/50 bg-card/30 p-8 backdrop-blur-sm transition-all duration-500 hover:border-primary/40 hover:bg-card/60 md:row-span-2">
				<div class="mb-6 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary/10 text-primary transition-colors group-hover:bg-primary/20">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="font-display text-2xl tracking-wide">ОНЛАЙН КОУЧИНГ</h3>
				<p class="mt-4 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
					Комплексный план тренировок и питания, анализ техники по видео, постоянная связь и отчётность. Полное сопровождение, где бы вы ни находились.
				</p>
				<div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
					<span class="rounded-full border border-primary/20 bg-primary/5 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-primary">Видеоразборы</span>
					<span class="rounded-full border border-primary/20 bg-primary/5 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-primary">План питания</span>
					<span class="rounded-full border border-primary/20 bg-primary/5 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-primary">24/7 поддержка</span>
				</div>
				<!-- Decorative gradient -->
				<div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-32 bg-linear-to-t from-primary/5 to-transparent opacity-0 transition-opacity group-hover:opacity-100"></div>
			</div>

			<!-- Card 2: Personal Training -->
			<div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-border/50 bg-card/30 p-8 backdrop-blur-sm transition-all duration-500 hover:border-primary/40 hover:bg-card/60">
				<div class="mb-6 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary/10 text-primary transition-colors group-hover:bg-primary/20">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="font-display text-xl tracking-wide">ПЕРСОНАЛЬНЫЕ ТРЕНИРОВКИ</h3>
				<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
					Очные занятия с разбором техники, мотивацией и максимальной эффективностью каждой минуты.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Card 3: Hybrid -->
			<div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-border/50 bg-card/30 p-8 backdrop-blur-sm transition-all duration-500 hover:border-primary/40 hover:bg-card/60">
				<div class="mb-6 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary/10 text-primary transition-colors group-hover:bg-primary/20">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15" />
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="font-display text-xl tracking-wide">ГИБРИДНЫЙ ФОРМАТ</h3>
				<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
					Комбинация онлайн и очных тренировок. Идеально для тех, кто хочет максимум.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Card 4: CTA card with anatomy image -->
			<div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-primary/30 bg-linear-to-br from-primary/10 to-accent/5 backdrop-blur-sm transition-all duration-500 hover:border-primary/50 md:col-span-2">
				<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-6 p-8">
					<div class="flex-1">
						<h3 class="font-display text-2xl tracking-wide">ПОДРОБНОСТИ<br/>О ПРОГРАММЕ</h3>
						<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
							Узнайте детали и стоимость каждого формата тренировок
						</p>
						<a
							href="#catalog"
							class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-linear-to-r from-brand-orange to-brand-gold px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-background transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(255,132,0,0.3)]"
						>
							Смотреть каталог
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
							</svg>
						</a>
					</div>
					<div class="w-40 shrink-0 sm:w-48">
						<Image
							src={anatomyImg}
							alt="Анатомия мышц"
							class="w-full drop-shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(255,132,0,0.3)]"
							widths={[200, 400]}
							sizes="200px"
						/>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
